dimension_like.label: Spot Rate Event Automated Strike Price Win Probability
dimension_like.name: price_requests_spot_rate_event.automated_strike_price_win_probability

queryResponse.sql:
-- use existing price_requests_last in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV3UT1659475262789_price_requests_last
-- use existing shipment_price_request_matches in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVMY71659475272387_shipment_price_request_matches
-- use existing shipment_base_accessorial_rate in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVTDW1659475260111_shipment_base_accessorial_rate
SELECT
    price_requests_spot_rate_event.automated_strike_price_win_probability AS "prsre.automated_strike_price_win_probability"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.custom_trunc_price_requests  AS price_requests
INNER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV3UT1659475262789_price_requests_last AS price_requests_last ON price_requests_last.price_request_id = price_requests.price_request_id and
      price_requests_last.shipper_application_id = price_requests.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN transfix_web_prod.transfix_marketplace_events_tables.spot_rates_event_1_table  AS price_requests_spot_rate_event ON (price_requests_spot_rate_event."EVENT_PRICE_REQUEST_ID")=price_requests.price_request_id and (case when coalesce(price_requests_spot_rate_event.synthetic_rate, price_requests_spot_rate_event.synthetic_dat_rate) = 'true' then true else false end) = 'false'
LEFT JOIN "RECREATED_TABLES"."SPOT_BIDDING_CONFIG_SHIPPER_GROUPS"
     AS spot_bidding_config_shipper_groups ON (spot_bidding_config_shipper_groups."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID") = price_requests.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.spot_bidding_configs  AS spot_bidding_configs ON (spot_bidding_configs."ID")=(spot_bidding_config_shipper_groups."SPOT_BIDDING_CONFIG_ID")
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON price_requests.shipper_application_id = shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVMY71659475272387_shipment_price_request_matches AS shipment_price_request_matches ON (shipment_price_request_matches."PRICE_REQUEST_ID")=price_requests.id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments ON shipments.id=(shipment_price_request_matches."SHIPMENT_ID") and (shipments.state not in ('canceled','e_submitted') and shipments.is_tonu!='true' and shipments.shipper_application_id != 625)
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVTDW1659475260111_shipment_base_accessorial_rate AS shipment_base_accessorial_rate ON shipment_base_accessorial_rate.shipment_id =  shipments.id
WHERE (price_requests.created_at ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 0, DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND (((( price_requests.created_at  ) >= (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-03-01') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))) AND ( price_requests.created_at  ) < (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-04-01') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AND (NOT (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) OR (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) IS NULL)) AND ((iff((nullif(price_requests.external_id, '')) is null, true, coalesce(price_requests_last.is_last_priced,false)) ) AND (coalesce(price_requests_spot_rate_event.STRATEGY_CHOSEN_NAME, 'default_spot_control_panel_configs') ) = 'automated_strike_price' AND (((shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Anheuser-Busch' AND ((shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Kraft-Heinz' AND (shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Recon Logistics') AND ((shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Odyssey' AND ((shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Odyssey Logisitics' AND (shipper_applications.name ) <> 'Leaf Logistics')) OR (shipper_applications.name ) IS NULL) AND (price_requests.source not in ('shipment_creation', 'auto_accept_reject') )))
GROUP BY
    1
HAVING AVG(( (case
        when price_requests.source in ('am_quoting_tool', 'am_quoting_tool_bulk') then price_requests.quote_all_in
        when coalesce((iff(spot_bidding_configs.rate_type='', 'ALL_IN', iff(spot_bidding_configs.rate_type='', 'LINEHAUL', spot_bidding_configs.rate_type)))='ALL_IN', true) then price_requests.customer_quote -- if there's no matching config, assume All In.
        else price_requests.customer_quote+(coalesce(price_requests.quote_all_in-price_requests.quote_line_haul,0))
      end
)/nullif(price_requests.dat_rate,0)   ) ) IS NOT NULL AND AVG(( (coalesce( ((case
        when shipments.is_tonu then null
        when shipments.shipper_application_id=1681 then shipments.shipper_rate + coalesce(shipment_base_accessorial_rate.base_accessorials_rate,0)
        else shipments.shipper_rate
      end)+(iff(shipments.is_tonu, 0, coalesce(shipments.shipper_total_fuel_surcharge, (coalesce(case when shipments.is_tonu then null else shipments.shipper_per_mile_fuel_rate end,0))*coalesce(shipments.shipper_miles,shipments.calculated_miles))))), price_requests.price_won ))/nullif(price_requests.dat_rate,0)   ) ) IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    1
FETCH NEXT 5000 ROWS ONLY
